{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Create a \u2018Day of Rest\u2019 in each calendar week as we come out lockdown.",
        "additional_details": "To return to having a day of rest where planes, trains and transport systems were halted for 24hrs, where businesses and schools  re charged through \u2018stopping\u2019 and allowed employees and pupils to rejuvenate or work from home.\r\nCarbon emissions targets would surely be more obtainable.\r\nThis doesn\u2019t have to be based on the old model of a religious day of rest, but of course those who wish to return to still contemplation and prayer could do so. It would be more powerful as an international movement.",
        "background": "The lockdown has proved that we as a nation can not only survive but also thrive when we\u2019re forced to Slow down and bring about a natural pause or stop in our busy lives. The environment and wild animal species have been allowed in many respects to return to \u2018their normal\u2019 as pollution levels drop.",
